al-tone-stryve-480x518.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 491px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<h2>Conversational tone: get on it<\/h2>\n<p>Whether it&#8217;s an ad, landing page, homepage, social post, or more, check to see if any of your copy could use a conversational facelift. You can always A\/B test one version against the other. The bottom line? Don&#8217;t take yourself too seriously. Loosen up the reigns a bit and see what comes to mind!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Learn how to write marketing copy that your audience actually wants to read.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":87,"featured_media":60883,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"_et_pb_use_builder":"","_et_pb_old_content":"","_et_gb_content_width":"","om_disable_all_campaigns":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[17],"tags":[],"dipi_cpt_category":[],"class_list":["post-58929","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-copywriting"],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v25.8 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>How to Write in Conversational Tone (+30 Awesome Examples)<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Find out what conversational tone is, why you should use it and how, plus 30+ examples of conversational copywriting that works.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/05\/05\/conversational-tone\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"How to Write in Conversational Tone (+30 Awesome Examples)\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Find out what conve